data.name: BBMMusic.ToolTip
data.value: You and your friends already share so much, why not share your favorite songs? BBM Music lets you discover the tunes your friends are listening to and lets them enjoy your songs too. Share and play full tracks on your BlackBerry® smartphone, so you can connect on a whole new level.
